в”ңв”Җв”Җ app/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ config.py          # VariГЎveis de configuraГ§ГЈo (URLs, caminhos, etc)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ core/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ downloader.py  # LГіgica central: download de YouTube вҶ’ MP3
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ routes/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ download.py    # Endpoints HTTP POST/GET para downloads
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ schemas/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ download.py    # Modelos Pydantic (validaГ§ГЈo de inputs)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ services/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ youtube.py     # ServiГ§o de gerenciamento de downloads
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ cleanup.py     # Limpeza automГЎtica de arquivos antigos
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ utils/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ id_generator.py # Gera IDs Гәnicos (timestamps + hash)
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ validators.py   # FunГ§Гөes de validaГ§ГЈo (URLs, etc)
